snippet.title: Aquaman Sicily set filming Mera rooftop run breakdown
snippet.description:
Aquaman filming on Village Roadshow Studios back lot of Joanna Bennett doubling for Amber Heard's Mera character doing wirework rooftop run trying to evade Atlantian Commandos. Two cameras can be seen during rehearsal and filming. This reproduction of a Sicily village has now been struck, no doubt it will be gone by the end of the week.
